1982;;An Unsuitable Job for a Woman;;British;;Chris Petit;;Billie Whitelaw, Paul Freeman;;crime;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/An_Unsuitable_Job_for_a_Woman_(film);;After finding her former boss, a private detective, is dead and has left her his agency, Cordelia Gray is asked to investigate the suicide of the man's son. She becomes obsessed with the boy and his suspicious death.